fy_Senso

Dedicated to: b2|Senso
	(Senso, your a true Gangsta)


Map Description:

fy_senso is exactly like fy_iceworld, except it is indoors in a school like eviroment.  

Up to 24 players can play at once but is better for 16 players (8v8)

The center of the map is a buyzone and you can shoot the ground to reveal a underground room
of sorts.  

You can climb on top of the classrooms anywhere you see a vent. Be aware that the main ceiling
is to low to jump from ceiling to ceiling.  This is no mistake but done in an effort to shorten
round times be avoiding a standoff where players can't find each other.

This is my first map that I am posting for download on the net.  If you got suggestions or Ideas for
new maps, please email me at Spartacus415@optonline.net
You will be given credit for advice and ideas.  Make sure to subject your email starting with *MAP Suggestion/Idea*
